name: SUPER FAQMAN - DEMO
description:
See the roadmap for the full game and support me here, if you like what I make:

The Wizard And The Frog - Patreon

A platformer where jumps is not unlimited as usually.

Get to the top as cleverly as you can! If you run out of jumps, the spikes will get you! Comment your score!

This is just a demo with the first level. Write a comment and tell me what you think <3
